"file_path":"/f0I1IUmNBXtxWimsWwDszFnzqFL.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.066},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/bNdP5MPz3eWFY3MB1inrA8IxhAl.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/wMRSaOcwe2VzFaTPtLIMP8Loh8g.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/6Uh9NJjcZPESoFgloSi15KswyjG.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/qc8mT348gNr6tQFuuEXiywlPqsi.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/iUhHHkA7M14xjb0FApPRBjDnKmN.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/pLJble74Fviz6d4XYaQxe9XeWxD.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":2048,"height":1152,"file_path":"/wICODxlPEoRVb7o57esaTKQe6IE.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1366,"height":768,"file_path":"/l5SoDsBVAkrBFqTHvIA0sth1WIR.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.222},{"width":1366,"height":768,"file_path":"/8tkNXR8EReTzfDONnLrmRoJ1DtO.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.222}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:19:19.203+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Hard Boiled","runtime":126,"tagline":"As a cop, he has brains, brawn, and an instinct to kill.","homepage":"https://gkids.com/golden-princess/hard-boiled/","overview":"A cop who loses his partner in a shoot-out with gun smugglers goes on a mission to catch them. In order to get closer to the leaders of the ring he joins forces with an undercover cop who's working as a gangster hitman. They use all means of excessive force to find them."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Hard Boiled","runtime":126,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Der Polizist Yuen gerät in ein undurchsichtiges Drogen- und Waffenhandels-Komplott. Ein Kampf Gut gegen Böse beginnt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"À toute épreuve","runtime":130,"tagline":"En tant que flic, il a l’intelligence, la musculature et l’instinct de tuer.","homepage":"","overview":"En 1997, alors que les Britanniques sont sur le point de rendre à la Chine une Hong‐Kong gangrénée par le crime, et alors que bien des policiers ont baissé les bras, un groupe d’inspecteurs inflexibles mené par « Tequila » Yuen décide de mettre fin à la suprématie des gangs."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Hard Boiled","runtime":128,"tagline":"Per essere un buon poliziotto devi avere muscoli, cervello... e l'istinto omicida.","homepage":"","overview":"Durante un'azione di polizia in una sala da tè, perde la vita un agente amico di Tequila (Chow Yun-fat). La sete di vendetta di quest'ultimo lo porterà involontariamente a ostacolare i piani dell'agente Alan (Tony Leung), infiltrato nell'organizzazione del sadico trafficante d'armi Johnny (Anthony Wong)."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Hervidero","runtime":126,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"El inspector Tequila Yuen (Chow Yun-Fat) es un duro policía encargado de detener una operación de contrabando de armas y de encontrar al asesino de su compañero. John Woo continúa con su personal estilo de violencia casi poética y tiroteos con ritmo en un thriller que cuenta con numerosos seguidores, toda una cinta de culto dentro del cine de acción. En España se estrenó en el año 1995, resultando un fracaso en taquilla."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Hard Boiled","runtime":128,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Inspecteur Yuen, alias Tequila is een politieagent die vanuit zijn heupen schiet, nooit laadt... en nooit mist. Een stoere gast met een groot hart en veel charme. Tequila is de enige die het gespuis in de stad kan opruimen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Круто сваренные","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Гонконгская полиция пытается противостоять триадам, контролирующим незаконный оборот оружия. Главный герой, полицейский по прозвищу Текила, хочет в одиночку обезвредить преступников и отомстить за убитого напарника…"},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Fervura Máxima","runtime":0,"tagline":"Como policial, ele tem cérebro, força e instinto para matar.","homepage":"","overview":"Em Hong Kong, Yuen (Chow Yun-Fat), um inspector da polícia que é normalmente conhecido como Tequila, fica transtornado quando o seu parceiro morre num tiroteio com gangsters numa casa de chá. Então Tequila une-se a Alan, um assassino profissional, para vingar o amigo e impedir que esta quadrilha mate gente inocente."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"辣手神探","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"袁浩云（周润发 饰）是一位办案勇猛、对朋友极讲义气的“辣手神探”，屡破奇案。他的目标是一个庞大的非法军火集团。该集团原由海叔（关海山 饰）掌控，但随着海叔年事已高，其势力被心狠手辣的新头目汪东源（黄秋生 饰）逐步取代。\r 警方卧底江浪（梁朝伟 饰）原是海叔的得力左右手。为取得汪东源的绝对信任，以便深入核心获取犯罪证据，江浪不得不亲手干掉海叔，以证明自己的“不二之心”。汪东源大喜，随即吸纳江浪为其头号马仔。\r 不知内情的袁浩云，将已成为黑帮核心的江浪视为必须铲除的死敌，两人多次交锋，拼得你死我活。然而，在激烈的对抗中，袁浩云逐渐察觉此人身份极可疑。最终，他得知江浪竟是身负重任的卧底同僚。\r 于是，一明一暗、性格迥异的两位警察——火爆直接的袁浩云与隐忍压抑的江浪，在身份揭露后决定联手。他们从生死相搏的对手，转变为背靠背作战的生死之交，共同向汪东源的军火帝国发起一场惊心动魄的终极决战。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Dzieci Triady","runtime":126,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Inspektor Yuen (Chow Yun-Fat) to twardy policjant, który poprzysiągł oczyścić miasto z wszystkich gangsterów. Alan (Tony Leung) to policjant, który też chce likwidować gangsterów. Jednak robi to od środka, jako jeden z członków gangu. Czasami musi łamać prawo, by udowodnić członkom triady, że jest po ich stronie. Chociaż obaj się różnią w sposobie działania, to jednak razem łączą swoje siły, by dokonać pełnej likwidacji wrogów społeczeństwa...  [opis dystrybutora dvd]"},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Hard Boiled","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Den hårdkokte Hong Kong-polisen Tequila förlorade sin partner i en eldstrid med vapensmugglare, och måste nu samarbeta med Tony (en polis som infiltrerat maffian) för att stoppa vapensmugglarna."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Sert Polis","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Polis memuru Yuen, ortağını kanlı bir saldırıda kaybeder ve onu intikamını almak için yemin eder. Kanunlarla bir şeyin çözülmediğini gören, Yuen intikamını almak için kendisi gibi düşünen Tony ile bir ekip olur. Silah kaçakçılığı yapan ve ortağını öldüren gangsterlerden intikam almak için büyük bir aksiyon-macera başlar * Aksiyon filmlerinin yaşayan en büyük ustalarından biri olan John Woo, ABD'ye transfer olmadan önce çektiği son Hong Kong yapımı filmidir. Bu Film John Woo'nun en iyi filmlerinden biri olarak gösterilmektedir..."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Hard Boiled","runtime":126,"tagline":"Největší akční divočina všech dob!!!","homepage":"","overview":"Hongkongské obyvatelstvo je terorizováno nebezpečnými gangstery a brutálními triádami. Policejní inspektor Yuen přísahá, že prohnilé podsvětí vyčistí. Na pomoc mu přichází tajný policista Tony. Oba muži, oddaní stejnému poslání ale každý zvyklý hrát jinak, spojí své síly, aby se pokusili vyhrát boj proti nenáviděnému nepříteli."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"첩혈속집","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"경찰관 데킬라는 불법무기거래 장면을 목격하고 싸우다 친구 아룡이 사망하게 된다. 이때 암흑가 무기밀매 조직의 일원이 암살당한 사건을 맡게 되는데, 조직의 대부 호이의 명령에 의해 아랑이 살해한 것이다. 한편 호이의 라이벌 조직인 쟈니왕은 아랑을 불러 호이와 데킬라의 암살을 제의한다. 호이는 결국 아랑의 총에 죽고, 아랑은 궁지에 몰린 데킬라를 살려주고 떠나는데, 사실 아랑은 그 조직에 침투한 비밀경찰이었다. 데킬라와 아랑은 진한 우.."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"A fegyverek istene","runtime":126,"tagline":"A \"Tökéletes Célpont\" és a \"Bérgyilkos\" rendezőjétől.","homepage":"","overview":"Yuen hírhedten kemény zsaru. Miközben a rendőrség elszántan igyekszik felszámolni a hongkongi fegyvercsempész-hálózatot, Yuen társát egy bevetés során halálos lövés éri. Ezután keményen ráfekszik az ügyre és megpróbálja kibogozni a szálakat, melyek az alvilágban szembenálló két maffiacsaládhoz vezetnek Az ügy felgöngyölítése kilátástalannak tűnik, ám Yuen tudomást szerez róla, hogy a rendőrség egyik emberének, Tonynak sikerült beépülnie a Triádba. A két nyomozó összefog, és közösen veszi fel a harcot a vérszomjas Johnny Wong bandája ellen."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Polițistul tare","runtime":0,"tagline":"Ca polițist, el are creier, mușchi, și un instinct de a ucide.","homepage":"","overview":"Un polițist care își pierde partenerul într-un împușcătură cu traficanții de arme, merge într-o misiune pentru a-i prinde. Pentru a se apropia de conducătorii inelului, el  își unește forțele cu un polițist sub acoperire, care lucrează ca un asasin pentru gangsteri. Ei folosesc toate mijloacele de forță excesivă pentru a-i găsi."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Fervura Máxima","runtime":128,"tagline":"Como policial, ele tem cérebro, força e instinto para matar.","homepage":"","overview":"Em Hong Kong, Yuen, um inspetor de polícia que é normalmente conhecido como Tequila, fica transtornado quando seu parceiro morre em um tiroteio com gângsters em uma casa de chá. Tequila então se une a Alan, um assassino profissional, para vingar o amigo e impedir que esta quadrilha mate gente inocente."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"سرسخت","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"هنگ کنگ. بازرس پلیس، «یوئن» (یون - فات)، در می‌یابد که «تونی» (لئونگ)، یکی از مردان دار و دسته‌ی «جانی وونگ» (وونگ) تبهکار معروف، در واقع یک پلیس مخفی است..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Твърдо сварен","runtime":128,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"В къща в центъра на Хонк Конг, полицейския офицер Йен и партньора му Бени са на път да арестуват група трафиканти на оръжия, които извършват важна сделка. Но след изненадващата намеса на друга престъпна банда, Йен и Бени попадат в центъра на яростна престрелка между полицията и двете групировки. След престрелката, оцелелите престъпници са арестувани, но има много ранени полицаи сред които и Бени, който не след дълго умира от раните си. Йен решава да отмъсти на отговорния за престрелката мафиотски бос, но не получава подкрепата на началника си Панг."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"À toute épreuve","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En 1997, alors que les Britanniques sont sur le point de rendre à  la Chine une Hong-Kong gangrénée par le crime, et alors que bien des policiers ont baissé les bras, un groupe d'inspecteurs inflexibles mené par 'Tequila' Yuen décide de mettre fin à  la suprématie des gangs."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"辣手神探","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"袁浩雲（周潤發 飾）是一位辦案勇猛、對朋友極講義氣的“辣手神探”，屢破奇案。他的目標是一個龐大的非法軍火集團。該集團原由海叔（關海山 飾）掌控，但隨著海叔年事已高，其勢力被心狠手辣的新頭目汪東源（黃秋生 飾）逐步取代。\r 警方臥底江浪（梁朝偉 飾）原是海叔的得力左右手。為取得汪東源的絕對信任，以便深入核心獲取犯罪證據，江浪不得不親手幹掉海叔，以證明自己的“不二之心”。汪東源大喜，隨即吸納江浪為其頭號馬仔。\r 不知內情的袁浩雲，將已成為黑幫核心的江浪視為必須剷除的死敵，兩人多次交鋒，拼得你死我活。然而，在激烈的對抗中，袁浩雲逐漸察覺此人身份極可疑。最終，他得知江浪竟是身負重任的臥底同僚。\r 於是，一明一暗、性格迥異的兩位警察——火爆直接的袁浩雲與隱忍壓抑的江浪，在身份揭露後決定聯手。他們從生死相搏的對手，轉變為背靠背作戰的生死之交，共同向汪東源的軍火帝國發起一場驚心動魄的終極決戰。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"鎗神","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"袁浩雲（周潤發 飾）是一位辦案勇猛、對朋友極講義氣的“辣手神探”，屢破奇案。他的目標是一個龐大的非法軍火集團。該集團原由海叔（關海山 飾）掌控，但隨著海叔年事已高，其勢力被心狠手辣的新頭目汪東源（黃秋生 飾）逐步取代。\r 警方臥底江浪（梁朝偉 飾）原是海叔的得力左右手。為取得汪東源的絕對信任，以便深入核心獲取犯罪證據，江浪不得不親手幹掉海叔，以證明自己的“不二之心”。汪東源大喜，隨即吸納江浪為其頭號馬仔。\r 不知內情的袁浩雲，將已成為黑幫核心的江浪視為必須剷除的死敵，兩人多次交鋒，拼得你死我活。然而，在激烈的對抗中，袁浩雲逐漸察覺此人身份極可疑。最終，他得知江浪竟是身負重任的臥底同僚。\r 於是，一明一暗、性格迥異的兩位警察——火爆直接的袁浩雲與隱忍壓抑的江浪，在身份揭露後決定聯手。他們從生死相搏的對手，轉變為背靠背作戰的生死之交，共同向汪東源的軍火帝國發起一場驚心動魄的終極決戰。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Hard Boiled","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Hard Boiled adalah sebuah film aksi tahun 1992. Film ini disutradarai dan ditulis oleh John Woo dengan co-penulis Barry Wong"},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Hard Boiled","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Triaderne, kinesiske gangstere, smugler våben ind i Hong Kong. Under en razzia på et te-hus mister en hårdkogt strømer sin partner, og sværger hævn. Sammen med en undercover betjent, som bliver sat ind some lejemorder for gangsterne, sætter han sig for at lukke hele organisationen ned."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"ทะลักจุดแตก","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เพราะการเข้าจับกุมคนร้ายผิดพลาดที๋โรงน้ำชา เป็นเหตุให้เบนนี่ เพื่อนรักของเตกีล่าตาย และเตกีล่ายังฆ่าตำรวจที่เป็นสายลับไปโดยไม่รู้ตัวทำให้เขามุ่งมั่นกับการตามจับตัวจอห์นนี่ หังหน้าแก๊งค์ลับลอบค้าอาวุธรายใหญ่ของฮ่องกง ระหว่างการตามล่าตัวจอห์นนี่เตกีล่าได้เจออลันตำรวจลับอีกคนที่ผู้กำกับปังส่งเข้าไปเป็นสายในแวดวงค้าอาวุธ เตกีล่าสงสัยว่าอลันจะเป็นตำรวจลับ และได้แอบติดต่อและตกลงกับอลันว่าจะร่วมมือกันจับตัวจอห์นนี่"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Ο Τιμωρός του Χονγκ Κονγκ","runtime":0,"tagline":"Ως αστυνομικός έχει το μυαλό, τα κότσια και την ιδιότητα να σκοτώνει","homepage":"","overview":"Ο Τεκίλα, ένας σκληροτράχηλος μπάτσος, συνεργάζεται με έναν μυστικό αστυνομικό προκειμένου να εξαρθρώσει το κύκλωμα παράνομου εμπορίου όπλων και ταυτόχρονα να εκδικηθεί το θάνατο του προηγούμενου συνεργάτη του."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"მაგრად მოხარშული","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ჰონკონგის პოლიცია ცდილობს წინ აღუდგეს დაჯგუფებას, რომელიც იარაღის უკანონო ვაჭრობაშია ჩართული.მთავარი გმირი, პოლიციელი- ტეკილა, ცდოლობს მარტომ აღკვეთოს დამნაშავეთა ქმედებები და შური იძიოს დაღუპულ მეწყვილეზე."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Lạt Thủ Thần Thám","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Hard boiled, hay còn có tên là God of guns (hoặc Hot-handed God of cops), là một câu chuyện về hai người cảnh sát, một nổi một chìm có chung một mục đích. Tequila (Châu Nhuận Phát) mất đi người bạn thân Benny trong một cuộc đọ súng dữ dội với băng nhóm tội phạm. Anh quyết trả thù cho bạn bằng cách của mình thay vì tìm bằng chứng để đưa chúng ra chịu tội trước pháp luật, bất chấp sự ngăn cản của cấp trên. Còn Alan (Lương Triều Vĩ) là một cảnh sát chìm hoạt động trong thế giới ngầm. Vì nhiệm vụ, Alan phải xuống tay với một ông trùm già và đám đàn em để chạy sang băng nhóm khác do Wong cầm đầu. Đây cũg chính là băng nhóm có liên quan tới cái chết của Benny. Trong khi Tequila muốn trả thù Wong thì Alan cũng muốn hắn đền tội để đỡ ..."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Круто Зварені","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Суворий коп об'єднується з агентом під прикриттям, щоб зупинити зловісного мафіозі та його банду."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Hard-Boiled","runtime":128,"tagline":"Como policía, tiene inteligencia, fuerza y un instinto para matar.","homepage":"","overview":"El inspector Tequila Yuen es un duro policía encargado de detener una operación de contrabando de armas y de encontrar al asesino de su compañero. John Woo continúa con su personal estilo de violencia casi poética y tiroteos con ritmo en un thriller que cuenta con numerosos seguidores, toda una cinta de culto dentro del cine de acción. En España se estrenó en el año 1995, resultando un fracaso en taquilla."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Kruti policaj","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Policist z vzdevkom Tequila bije neusmiljen boj proti mreži prekupčevalcev orožja. Ko v krvavem obračunu v čajni hiši izgubi svojega partnerja, ga maščevalna sla pripelje do “gangsterja” Alana, ki se izkaže za policijskega agenta pod krinko. Skupaj se spopadeta z brezkompromisnim kriminalnim imperijem in pri tem ne izbirata sredstev. Njun lov na pravico ju vodi skozi eksplozivno okolje, v katerem se lahko vsak korak hitro izkaže za zadnjega."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"64b774c4d399e6012db4b056","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/64b774c4d399e6012db4b056","author":"Filipe Manuel Neto","content":"$11","created_at":"2023-07-19T05:29:40.969Z","updated_at":"2023-07-19T05:29:41.090Z","author_details":{"name":"Filipe Manuel Neto","rating":1,"username":"FilipeManuelNeto","avatar_path":"/nidqITf735x9xxHfncXkT9BmOQ7.png"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":10835,"adult":false,"title":"The Killer","video":false,"overview":"Mob assassin Jeffrey is no ordinary hired gun; the best in his business, he views his chosen profession as a calling rather than simply a job. So, when beautiful nightclub chanteuse Jennie is blinded in the crossfire of his most recent hit, Jeffrey chooses to retire after one last job to pay for his unintended victim's sight-restoring operation. But when Jeffrey is double-crossed, he reluctantly joins forces with a rogue policeman to make things right.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1724,"vote_count":867,"poster_path":"/8hTxlSqMAHBXAh1eB69ir0BXhzE.jpg","release_date":"1989-03-24","vote_average":7.596,"backdrop_path":"/z8zZouMO4vvRNVAwexgMbaIgxYe.jpg","original_title":"喋血雙雄","original_language":"cn"},{"id":29621,"adult":false,"title":"Solo","video":false,"overview":"An android fighting-machine is charged with destroying a small brigade of rebels in a Latin American war who are fighting to maintain their freedom and protect their village. Contrary to his programming, Peebles decides to stay and assist the rebels in their plight. Having gained this information, his \"creators\" develop a more powerful android to try and defeat him.","genre_ids":[28,12,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9006,"vote_count":83,"poster_path":"/9qqdpyYVnU5zY5KsTKCIp5gpZoV.jpg","release_date":"1996-08-23","vote_average":4.813,"backdrop_path":"/vuYYs28DH51wM9UAdJNcnvy14LS.jpg","original_title":"Solo","original_language":"en"},{"id":356161,"adult":false,"title":"Phantom Boy","video":false,"overview":"At a hospital in New York, Alex, a police officer, meets Leo, a boy who has the ability to get out of his body and pass through the walls like a ghost. Both team up with Mary, an intrepid journalist, to capture a disfigured villain who terrorizes the city.","genre_ids":[16,14,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4671,"vote_count":73,"poster_path":"/AlCyvatuIXehWMFrhqR4QE1ZIt.jpg","release_date":"2015-10-14","vote_average":7.021,"backdrop_path":"/laQAm6xswJQBb5KAfS7H3rPh1Bk.jpg","original_title":"Phantom Boy","original_language":"fr"},{"id":11539,"adult":false,"title":"Don Camillo","video":false,"overview":"A priest helps the small town he's stationed in to resolve conflicts by working together.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6392,"vote_count":87,"poster_path":"/b5KoVB3zdDY99lvry2OZKtpbVR1.jpg","release_date":"1984-02-08","vote_average":5.586,"backdrop_path":"/rR9JZAbxDaG5k1vxy1wNlYIUukT.jpg","original_title":"Don Camillo","original_language":"it"},{"id":20309,"adult":false,"title":"Say It Isn't So","video":false,"overview":"Boy meets girl; boy falls in love (and had wild, non-stop sex) with girl; boy loses girl... when they discover they are brother and sister! But when he learns that he's the victim of the ultimate case of mistaken identity, the lovesick young man -- whom everyone still thinks is after some taboo thrills -- must race across the country to stop her from marrying another man.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8204,"vote_count":178,"poster_path":"/gHEI41EWj9dEscfEiKgw6a2uUez.jpg","release_date":"2001-03-10","vote_average":4.7,"backdrop_path":"/fNb6NSwfv76je5MQp58rvJxvoMU.jpg","original_title":"Say It Isn't So","original_language":"en"},{"id":32166,"adult":false,"title":"Chasing Sleep","video":false,"overview":"A college professor wakes up to find his wife has not returned home, then struggles to understand her disappearance.","genre_ids":[27,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4227,"vote_count":88,"poster_path":"/5pC2f3ewFmDV9KA6XbZLPx6tPb8.jpg","release_date":"2001-05-16","vote_average":5.983,"backdrop_path":"/bET2U7hMozQlSolyRcB508X5Erl.jpg","original_title":"Chasing Sleep","original_language":"en"},{"id":37749,"adult":false,"title":"Looking for Mr. Goodbar","video":false,"overview":"A short, unhappy affair with a married man leads a dedicated schoolteacher into the alcohol-and-drug fueled underworld of singles’ bars, where she begins to engage in a pattern of dangerous sexual activity.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1373,"vote_count":124,"poster_path":"/j1qKNKRvDEhnl0PQS26PirNF81v.jpg","release_date":"1977-10-19","vote_average":6.363,"backdrop_path":"/mN6xN0rz7BqfgMHsGYnmvD4EXfG.jpg","original_title":"Looking for Mr. Goodbar","original_language":"e