ell. The guys decide to head for taiga and catch bandits, but they still don't know that soon the bandits will kidnap the wife of Fyodor's brother and a newly arrived girl.","genre_ids":[28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1882,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/dLIO5L36LJLCr6fTPLnmU5uO2T9.jpg","release_date":"1982-12-06","vote_average":3.6,"backdrop_path":"/5bM8tStKufdfrx2DSNrg2CXRDuz.jpg","original_title":"Найти и обезвредить","original_language":"ru"},{"id":47212,"adult":false,"title":"China Girl","video":false,"overview":"Teenage lovers Tony and Tyan-Hwa tip the balance of power in New York's Little Italy and Chinatown.","genre_ids":[10749,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7515,"vote_count":70,"poster_path":"/x0VilySeyfLX3HSobjWv3CXxvCp.jpg","release_date":"1987-09-25","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/m0lmDVKbQ1TA9sQoUxgBorgFsI5.jpg","original_title":"China Girl","original_language":"en"},{"id":53426,"adult":false,"title":"The Evil That Men Do","video":false,"overview":"A former assassin (Charles Bronson) comes out of retirement to avenge the brutal murder of his friend at the hands of a sadistic torturer (Joseph Maher) employed by an oppressive foreign dictatorship.","genre_ids":[28,12,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.897,"vote_count":111,"poster_path":"/162uiSsFdiAF7B3My7O2mG6cjHW.jpg","release_date":"1984-03-14","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/yr8bQ7IZISm97WyGEqXakQd041J.jpg","original_title":"The Evil That Men Do","original_language":"en"},{"id":37835,"adult":false,"title":"The Exterminator","video":false,"overview":"When a man's best friend is killed on the streets of New York, he transforms into a violent killer, turning New York into a war zone.","genre_ids":[28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9633,"vote_count":143,"poster_path":"/8u49TsGXYYR3mkiuJ12GswGtkCA.jpg","release_date":"1980-09-10","vote_average":5.531,"backdrop_path":"/lmTbufMBEvi6ZNwvdbvz9wQkyXy.jpg","original_title":"The Exterminator","original_language":"en