ge":3.6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Wish You Were Here","original_language":"en"},{"id":2112,"adult":false,"title":"Payback","video":false,"overview":"With friends like these, who needs enemies? That's the question bad guy Porter is left asking after his wife and partner steal his heist money and leave him for dead -- or so they think. Five months and an endless reservoir of bitterness later, Porter's partners and the crooked cops on his tail learn how bad payback can be.","genre_ids":[28,18,80,53],"popularity":3.7685,"vote_count":1954,"poster_path":"/8Bqlv2kbOyZFqfiPNgzdBscqYPn.jpg","release_date":"1999-02-05","vote_average":6.82,"backdrop_path":"/nlppU9QYqqfrnVGYEgSsCHzgMr8.jpg","original_title":"Payback","original_language":"en"},{"id":2139,"adult":false,"title":"Cleopatra Jones and the Casino of Gold","video":false,"overview":"When fellow operatives and friends disappear during a mission in Hong Kong, Cleopatra Jones comes to help. She discovers the disappearance involves The Dragon Lady, a feared lipstick lesbian who runs a casino and the local drug trade.","genre_ids":[28,12,18],"popularity":0.4621,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/yqXTLGEnQ8wjo6RkzPOXY61WgVc.jpg","release_date":"1975-07-11","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/bJ1jD1wkVY7mX9RjHGDLoIY4ulf.jpg","original_title":"Cleopatra Jones and the Casino of Gold","original_language":"en"},{"id":2140,"adult":false,"title":"Kiss of the Dragon","video":false,"overview":"Liu Jian, an elite Chinese police officer, comes to Paris to arrest a Chinese drug lord. When Jian is betrayed by a French officer and framed for murder, he must go into hiding and find new allies.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":2.8551,"vote_count":1300,"poster_path":"/1ubtSyagwfNF9Bn9s2CKITRtx1d.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-06","vote_average":6.89,"backdrop_path":"/9S0BHQuZAyNMG0GpHAMSIbF38au.jpg","original_title":"Kiss of the Dragon","original_language":"en"},{"id":793,"adult":false,"title":"Blue Velvet","video":false,"overview":"The discovery of a severed human ear found in a field leads a young man on an investigation related to a beautiful, mysterious nightclub singer and a group of psychopathic criminals who have kidnapped her child.","genre_ids":[9648,53,80],"popularity":7.4411,"vote_count":3727,"poster_path":"/tzXuURjPzCqtA6eL0Cswq9wzFx0.jpg","release_date":"1986-09-19","vote_average":7.61,"backdrop_path":"/12UiL2rS5M80AhS9uiZ633iy4pB.jpg","original_title":"Blue Velvet","original_language":"en"},{"id":841,"adult":false,"title":"Dune","video":false,"overview":"In the year 10,191, the most precious substance in the universe is the spice Melange. The spice extends life. The spice expands consciousness. The spice is vital to space travel.  The spice exists on only one planet in the entire universe, the vast desert planet Arrakis, also known as Dune.  Its native inhabitants, the Fremen, have long held a prophecy that a man would come, a messiah who would lead them to true freedom.","genre_ids":[28,878,12],"popularity":6.5146,"vote_count":3340,"poster_path":"/4kJmUCE7mkVJjXa7A0g2rY4IGTm.jpg","release_date":"1984-12-14","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/5wJ2tckpvwcxGCAgZiccodwEJpf.jpg","original_title":"Dune","original_language":"en"},{"id":855,"adult":false,"title":"Black Hawk Down","video":false,"overview":"When U.S. Rangers and an elite Delta Force team attempt to kidnap two underlings of a Somali warlord, their Black Hawk helicopters are shot down, and the Americans suffer heavy casualties, facing intense fighting from the militia on the ground.","genre_ids":[28,10752,36],"popularity":6.2342,"vote_count":6213,"poster_path":"/7fU5dSqKRL4XHeEUz62rCKBfYok.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-28","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/o6f1sJ0ZYg6TA2tMgoHdupB68QB.jpg","original_title":"Black Hawk Down","original_language":"en"},{"id":407,"adult":false,"title":"Short Sharp Shock","video":false,"overview":"Gabriel, Bobby and Costa are old friends from Altona, a multicultural hood in Hamburg. Just out of prison, Gabriel wants to turn his back on crime, but the others continue to operate as petty criminals. Friendships are tested as the trio navigate a dark world of mafia bosses and deals gone wrong.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":0.3639,"vote_count":87,"poster_path":"/cVyYb5REN5cX5CWAr7wcdu7cT4Y.jpg","release_date":"1998-10-15","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/qOzN3bxxUgIMgkBNEhLKPqRcIWV.jpg","original_title":"Kurz und schmerzlos","original_language":"de"},{"id":471,"adult":false,"title":"Brute","video":false,"overview":"Shipped off to a Romanian orphanage to finish his sentence, a British criminal finds romance but also discovers corruption inside the facility.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":0.5518,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/fs5mushBGKZbt4ZaRjgfPBQKMRU.jpg","release_date":"1997-11-07","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/P3vdWKS2MgabHEolxCHM6RkUrW.jpg","original_title":"Bandyta","original_language":"pl"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0104684","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q573823","instagram_id":null,"mydramalist_id":"69","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/hard_boiled"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":102721,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1992-05-07T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"R 18+"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":5,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1994-11-01T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":5,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1993-04-15T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"18"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1995-06-09T00:00:00